<bibRefCitation author="Golani, D." box="[661,807,1729,1755]" pageId="70" pageNumber="71" pagination="1 - 108" refId="ref55342" refString="Golani, D. (2021) An updated checklist of the Mediterranean fishes of Israel, with illustrations of recently recorded species and delineation of Lessepsian migrants. Zootaxa, 4956 (1), 1 - 108. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 4956.1.1" type="journal article" year="2021">Golani 2021</bibRefCitation>
